      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 07:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及即将举行大选，塞西将在危机中开启新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/egypt-heads-to-polls-with-el-sisi-set-for-new-term-amid-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及人于周日开始为期三天的选举投票，随着这个北非国家努力摆脱多年来最严重的经济危机，总统阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西几乎肯定会赢得第三个任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/egypt-heads-to-polls-with-el-sisi-set-for-new-term-amid-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 07:05:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克从“Dishy Rishi”到“Dr. Covid 调查中的“死亡”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/sunak-s-shift-from-dishy-rishi-to-dr-death-faces-uk-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这张照片捕捉到了里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在疫情期间人气最高的情景：经过数月的惩罚性封锁后，时任英国财政部长微笑着端着两份咖喱猪排给等待的食客。 2020 年 7 月，在那家餐厅里，不太可能有人需要他的“Rishi”名牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/sunak-s-shift-from-dishy-rishi-to-dr-death-faces-uk-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港根据新规则举行首次立法会选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-10/hong-kong-holds-first-council-elections-under-new-rules-that-shut-out-pro-democracy-candidates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港（美联社）——周日，香港居民参加了自在北京“爱国者”管理香港的指导下实施选举改革以来的首次区议会选举，这实际上将所有亲民主候选人拒之门外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-10/hong-kong-holds-first-council-elections-under-new-rules-that-shut-out-pro-democracy-candidates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 03:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和菲律宾船只在第二天发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/hundreds-from-philippines-set-sail-as-tensions-flare-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[整个周末，中国和菲律宾船只在南海有争议海域连续发生冲突，两国海域领土争端紧张局势加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/hundreds-from-philippines-set-sail-as-tensions-flare-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 02:57:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相因资金丑闻解雇第二大臣：朝日新闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/japan-pm-to-fire-second-minister-in-funds-scandal-asahi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《朝日新闻》称，日本首相岸田文雄将解雇内阁第二名高级成员和多达三名执政党官员，因为贿赂资金丑闻威胁到了政府的生存能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-10/japan-pm-to-fire-second-minister-in-funds-scandal-asahi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 00:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
